*Mlad* čovek je počeo da radi u novoj firmi. (The *young* man started working at a new company.)

Ona je *mlada* i puna energije. (She is *young* and full of energy.)

*Mladi* ljudi su nadareni za učenje novih stvari. (*Young* people are gifted at learning new things.)

Oni su *mladi* par koji je upravo počeo da živi zajedno. (They are a *young* couple who have just started living together.)

Ona je *mlad* i zaljubljen u njenog dečka. (She is *young* and in love with her boyfriend.)